LIST
to list contents of dir

# ls : to list the files / direc in the present direc

# ls /path/to/direc/ : to list the files and direc in the target direc

# ls -l : to list the files / direcs in the long list format which provides additional info

# ls -a : to list files / direc along with the hidden files / direcs

# ls -la : to get the long listing of all the files / direc inc hidden 
